first_interaction.speaker: Station Lobby 1
first_interaction.text: Nakita mo ba si PO1 Darwin kanina? Mukhang stressed na stressed siya.

first_interaction.text: Oo nga! Laging may hawak na kape at nagsusulat sa notebook niya.

first_interaction.speaker: Station Lobby 1
first_interaction.text: Sabi nila may problema daw sa kaso ni Leo Mendoza. Ang daming inconsistencies.

first_interaction.speaker: Station Lobby 2
first_interaction.text: Kaya pala laging nagmamadali si PO1 Darwin. Baka may deadline sila.

first_interaction.speaker: Station Lobby 1
first_interaction.text: Pero hindi ka makakapasok dito. May mga bagay na kailangan naming gawin.

repeated_interaction.speaker: Station Lobby 1
